This package is licensed under the MIT License (below), and incorporates code
derived from the following MIT-licensed projects, whose license notices are
reproduced in full as required:

- vanilla-extract (https://github.com/vanilla-extract-css/vanilla-extract):
  the core `.css.ts` compilation plugin is a port of
  `@vanilla-extract/rollup-plugin`, combined with ideas from
  `@vanilla-extract/vite-plugin`.
- tsdown (https://github.com/rolldown/tsdown): the CSS collection and emission
  architecture, and the esbuild-style target conversion, are derived from
  `@tsdown/css`.

The plugin was originally published as `@sanity/vanilla-extract-tsdown-plugin`
before its rolldown-generic core was split into this package.

